# Harness Rules

For agent-side changes:
1. Add or update fixture cases.
2. Run the narrowest relevant harness.
3. Repair from failure logs.
4. Re-run the harness.

Expected commands:
```bash
make agent-fixtures
make agent-dry-run
make agent-check
```

Do not mark work complete if the harness has not run.
If the harness command does not exist yet, create it as part of the change.
